\backslash
textcite{Veblen89}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
textcite{duesenberry1949}
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 have been satiated,
 the dominant motivation becomes the accumulation of wealth in order to exert power and influence.
 In this case,
 accumulated wealth,
 in addition to providing security,
 provides power over others,
 and,
 if unchecked,
 the ability to alter the rules of the game of the socio-economic system,
 in favour of those possessing the most wealth (see for example 
\begin_inset ERT
